      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"8. OTTO ROSE hit the frame last time at Warragul but the start prior rocketed around 435m at this track in 24.50. Rates on top and can find winning form again. 3. HURRY DUSTY finds it hard to win. Finished second (29.25) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Expected to be in the finish again. 1. MAUDIE ROSE is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 0.8 lengths at Warragul in a handy 23.27 beating Runway Blue. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Should feature again. 4. APPLE ROSE can feature with the right run.\",\"runners\":[8,3,1,4],\"exclusive\":false}",
